name: BUST #2
description:
This project was designed and curated by Francesco Schito.
This is a series of 20 BUSTS sculpted on iPad using Forger app.
All the BUSTS are the work of the artist's imagination, they were made extemporaneously without any initial sketch.
They are the result of the artistic and emotional flow that inspired them, they were born while they were conceived.

None of these BUSTS are inspired by real people.

Each BUST is unique.
